        <strong class="slide-block">Tools/Techniques:</strong>
        <ul>
            <li>Copywriting
                <ul style="list-style: circle">
                    <li>Content library (for aligning new work with existing guidelines)</li>
                    <li>Google Trends (for generating SEO-optimized copy)</li>
                    <li>GatherContent (for staying organized)</li>
                </ul>
            </li>
            <li>Design
                <ul style="list-style: circle;">
                    <li>Style guide (for aligning new work with existing guidelines)</li>
                    <li>Photoshop (for creating/manipulating images)</li>
